OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fbreaking through the evening, with
OL,7,Fsome late sunny spells. Inland showers
OL,8,Feasing before cloud thickens
OL,9,Fovernight, with coastal showers and
OL,10,Flight winds continuing. Cold with a
OL,11,Fchance of frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,14,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,15,Fthrough the morning as frequent
OL,16,Fshowers spread west, these perhaps
OL,17,Fheavy in the afternoon. Winds
OL,18,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
