OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells on Tuesday. Dry but
OL,7,Fcloudy on Wednesday and Thursday,
OL,8,Fespecially near coasts. Breezy,
OL,9,Fparticularly over hills, feeling cool
OL,10,Fnear coasts. Chilly by night.
